{
  "logNo": "223931238893",
  "title": "자유로운 행택, 명함 모양을 만드세요. 색지에 백색 인쇄하시면 더 돋보입니다.",
  "date": "2025-07-15",
  "addDate": "2025. 7. 15.",
  "categoryNo": "78",
  "category": "표지/포스터/낱장",
  "source_url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223931238893",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8332da6e-c336-4afc-9a87-4fc3f90d163e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">모양 인쇄물 제작방법</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4d294b68-54f0-4f31-959e-6904c3cfb5de\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>모양 인쇄물은 자유로운 모양을 디지털로 커팅 하여 제작됩니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75d33c2b-58ed-4c2d-8519-7aecf65bb800\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 디지털 장비의 발달은 옛날 대량으로 목형을 만들어 제작하는 것을 많이 변화시켰습니다. 물론 종이나 사이즈, 또는 퀄리티에서 약간의 제약사항이 존재하지만 저렴하게 소량 생산을 해보고 싶으신 고객님이라면 딱 맞는 인쇄 유형입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a9247c4-369d-4ce6-86d7-f066c8297d04\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-17f9499b-d93c-4fde-bf0e-639d60e6f6c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-673dbc24-7247-4cf7-a51e-deb428cb2346\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9b1294d9-5abd-498d-a91c-8ea6191e7432\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>모양 인쇄물은 다음과 같은 준비 사항이 필요합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0978304-e2a5-4944-855a-7581aa365fbd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-516d5bb4-9dc3-45bb-9f6e-5de34a1fdbae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8c3a924-6aa7-49d6-a7bd-713085b8daf7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05c958e1-d26b-454d-9a5f-5f96f0992a83\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일단 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a4039246-cecf-4596-bf4a-80ec697d31d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41b66cd5-bfaf-44ae-8007-2b52cd8184a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">와 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-638c2a92-791d-4823-8737-8a488ec003ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>모양</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-290f0f77-28f2-4bea-b954-79dc1c3b4cf3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 정합니다. 사이즈를 정하고 따는 모양에 따라 금액이 결정됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-26aa6dfe-dcc2-4c40-b055-81a68a97015b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/001.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f856b11b-136f-49e2-8ec8-156155cd52ef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:721px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cdc17ecb-ff7c-4b9e-bea2-5bf83416da81\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8206b10a-4681-4c09-8e2e-21698e45b2ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-97c5cbb0-9633-4daf-84a6-f85f695d93bb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0eb071a7-81ae-4648-ae0a-5f7120fb60cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가로, 세로의 크기가 정해지고 그 안에서의 모양이 정해지면 일반적으로 자유형 모양의 택이든 명함이든 인쇄물의 견적이 준비된 것입니다. 반드시 가로, 세로 사이즈의 모양을 말해주시고 견적을 의뢰하시기 바랍니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cec8a965-700f-41d2-bc8c-1153aa8bdea7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">일반적으로는 단순한 모양인지, 복잡한 모양인지에 따라 인쇄물의 디지털 커팅 비용이 결정됩니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a08799d1-03b8-416c-9adf-4169b0057bcf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0224aea5-3cbe-434d-b457-4f65f39f2599\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-51aec18f-34cb-4651-8773-56da9616972c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5953fce-6ea1-43e7-96de-5207d3ad7060\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ab4c8db-5feb-4900-ad9a-4c0353a50253\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모양을 정할 때 주의점은 조밀하고 너무 복잡하게 제작하면 안 된다는 것입니다. 다음 글을 참고해 보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5635a953-9dfd-4ef2-ad0e-add3795c12e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e187c2ba-b606-4e93-ba67-4e0c8d81d472\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f71c8655-56a1-4a7a-aa0c-5c96c52c0be8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e54890ca-5b2f-4d29-84fc-33f227ae66e1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4ed0260-c10e-4800-bef0-8d722681e211\" style=\"color:#555555;\">간단히 설명하면 극 세밀한 모양은 커팅이 불가능하다는 것입니다. 그림으로 쉽게 설명하면 다음과 같은 내용입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffcf7d5e-47a5-4366-bf3f-e7b226aa221d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e25390c9-173c-4306-a879-4a95e49f663f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1fa1c180-2cdb-4706-82d8-42a0b561954d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-40879bf6-163c-4fee-8fa8-d73039f35688\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b91358d-9f3e-4054-a74d-78c3811012fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c80a4169-4cfb-480d-9325-65ff86bebca0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오른쪽 같은 모양은 커팅으로 했을 때 따지는 것을 떠나서 매우 위험한 작업입니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e2d20719-a6c2-466f-bf90-9d9dbd026859\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>반드시 모양을 정하거나 할 때는 (주)파파스컴퍼니에게 물어보시기 바랍니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-968e6ed1-9c71-44f3-b84c-21146613c832\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1e5fd4a-dea1-4108-8ad5-0659a12251dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-140204f6-f37b-400d-96db-cf2b20c347b1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea4a10eb-483c-40c8-b993-1dd8a860458e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8770112e-3ba3-48a3-a868-bd5fc366359c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-af347077-4236-4d50-858d-16800d12f573\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄 색상</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5383d245-f14d-482e-9bc5-157529e8fa98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에 따른 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a85cd009-6f97-40d3-91da-5efa2442c883\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-114cf5c0-98aa-4a05-b810-9dbe338f598d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 및 방법 설정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b79591f-e223-45a6-a2e7-b3d4f6f3af2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a21a8473-f8bf-4fd8-8725-9f4a7bb3e12b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 말은 컬러로 인쇄를 진행할지 아니면 색지에 백색 인쇄를 할지 또 이것도 아니면 독판으로 별색을 진행할지를 결정하는 것입니다. 일반 CMYK 인쇄로 진행을 하면 일반적인 모든 종이가 가능합니다. 하지만 백색 인쇄나 별색 인쇄의 경우 가능한 종이나 인쇄 방법이 따릅니다. 백색 인쇄는 시리오칼라 종이들이 잘 어울립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-89489912-e79d-49eb-8f85-1ae7a13c8939\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd78d0c1-3f17-4c3d-8bca-31bd0654c39f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b0fd05a0-f677-4516-ae24-091320a6aefa\" style=\"\">삼원페이퍼 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ee05de70-ae41-4fee-b572-06add39534c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e945012-4c88-44ae-8dad-5859e85161e5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-01837ce1-5039-4c2b-8da8-6867b1168dfd\" style=\"\">색지에 백색 인쇄를 하는 이유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3412dbfe-0730-4b0b-8975-34380763e855\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d8bdd4f-0945-4db7-bc87-ca3a0f51fef7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4d66650-4615-4265-9bae-c55d33c2fa0b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">색지에 백색 인쇄를 하는 이유는 명확합니다. 원래 4도 인쇄에서는 바탕의 빨간색을 인쇄로 처리하고 누끼로 하얀 글자를 표현합니다. 하지만 이렇게 진행하게 되면 특히 합판 인쇄에서는 인쇄를 발주할 때마다 약간(?)은 다른 색상으로 구현됩니다. 그렇기 때문에 바탕의 빨간색이 층짐 현상이 생길 수도 있고 재발주시 마다 색상이 달라지는 단점 때문입니다. 종이 자체를 색지로 작업하게 되면 동일한 인쇄물을 꾸준하게 얻을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08c3a29f-9c8f-4b9b-a819-5458148fa6b6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-956f51f2-6fd2-4a41-9659-4b5c73591e01\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8139ea4e-b813-408b-a0d6-366530136a72\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2830ed8c-1243-4f84-86c7-5b7481ffa36e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 색지에 백색 인쇄를 진행하여 통일된 인쇄 퀄리티를 유지하도록 합니다. 하지만 이렇게 진행해도 단점은 있습니다. 색지에 백색 인쇄를 하기 때문에 약간은 백색이 흐리게 인쇄될 수 있으며 다른 컬러 인쇄를 진행하는데 제약사항이 발생합니다. 특히 검은 색지에 컬러 인쇄는 거의 불가능하기 때문에 별색이나 백색밖에 안된다고 보시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a4b3697-d3d2-4a4e-aeba-d7b777ff09d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b6f8f0c-03a3-4d5b-a662-7981474e3ea1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-076b4b1d-e699-406f-b296-a3cbca2c7818\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c06c2889-a846-4837-ba86-361da8fc2046\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시리오나 색지 종이에 백색을 인쇄하고 290g 평량까지는 무난하게 디지털 커팅이 가능하므로 이렇게 제작하면 경제적으로 원하는 인쇄물을 얻으실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae791648-e859-45ce-9ddb-34658bdfa0ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6c6ec39-7d41-43cd-a8e9-28e1501a1008\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4af5f4dc-c59e-4736-b20e-e2d138402a71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f927e034-da42-4073-af2d-509817579e36\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-6011f3c4-531c-4dbe-88e6-898624baaecb\" style=\"\">다음이 고민이신 분은 연락 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c49bac1f-ce05-4258-8ca0-b0462a79f84a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc91c44e-8729-4fe5-b744-94d355f2e60d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5b61bebc-2c24-4b1e-8f8e-33847cd0e5fc\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>자신만의 독특한 모양 행택이 필요하신 분</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59272205-7389-4fe1-9529-515ff4aac636\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a707dffb-09a2-4866-9cba-2974d54beb7d\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>자신만의 통일된 색상이 꾸준히 나오기를 원하는 분</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ef8c044d-85dc-45ac-aa79-53f4b28217d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-73950563-0f52-45ed-89d5-fe1f6c160612\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>자신만의 독특한 명함이 필요하신 분</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd64f297-9b37-4b56-81c3-71c9b15d08fa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c85308cf-47a7-4017-916c-b0cb5bc547e8\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>소량 패키지 제작에 관심 있으신 분</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3442ced-38a3-4727-82d0-175a04708182\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0e3b3e1d-43a8-45c2-8230-550244c22ad9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-303e3386-dd04-46ec-84b1-3669af65fa20\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-554ab47a-0071-4342-8054-798f2d8f80ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 소량으로 모양 행택이나 명함을 제작하고 싶으신 분</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eafcdbbe-da78-4778-b8d3-31628cbdba9e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29a7cf96-76e3-4c6e-accc-141bd108e46a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-acc75e11-9373-45e5-b045-e36d1b73fc27\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-082a4e2a-55dc-4398-88ad-8c1d36d76369\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5bf996f-8960-4c03-8c4e-86df81cf4bad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c8503d1-90fe-486f-bd59-241a5b68c548\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-82c43360-e5b2-4072-8a80-1384b91f8fb2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 일반적인 모양이거나 다양한 명함 스타일을 원하실 때</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1274d33-f639-4f3d-8427-ff677e8a89f8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-911bd948-3ef1-4505-b4fd-5bcd18a81ee9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dcd2d5c6-ee71-443e-b7d0-55c5f680709a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aee910b0-a26e-42c7-b95b-4310d37b6ed5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9fd51a21-914c-416f-a038-2123aaf80d26\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\"><b>물론 디지털 커팅은 패키지 쪽에 더 특화돼서 작업할 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3327a99-9927-402d-9625-3eeb6c5e20a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-32b2816b-c15c-4996-88ce-a6b4916cee39\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8c8af9fa-b401-4203-8054-cb2a9b5d0d34\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e962ce92-836c-41f0-9b79-e003fc5b8ef9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dd397c4e-b9b1-467d-b4eb-5293dfc42c98\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 소량 디지털 패키지 작업에 특화된 업체입니다. 100개 미만 소량 패키지를 가장 합리적인 단가로 제공해 드립니다. 물론 사이즈나 종이 제약이 있으므로 반드시 문의하시고 작업을 진행하여 주시기 바랍니다.  고객님께서는 디자인 작업 유무, 사이즈, 수량만 고민하시고 나머지는 친절한 상담을 통해 결정하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d27ea1df-041e-40c6-bc48-5761b4c9e538\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7305168-e415-49d2-8648-f71853b4ec39\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71eeda20-72ba-4edf-a85f-330ed9d11075\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6e9a3208-3a51-4e36-87ef-debb423b51ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">24시간 365일 카톡이나 문의에 최선을 다하고 있습니다. 물론 본 영업시간 외에는 답변이 늦어질 수 있지만 최선을 다해 상담 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cfc5ff9-3fb1-4074-a7cd-ca5e7e5ee68d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86a35802-9595-4584-97b1-a58d61496755\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-364dcdda-6c07-42aa-a5f7-3f3628914ba6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223931238893/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79eba2a2-27d6-46f0-a2d7-3e8b209e30d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31c83cab-ab04-4137-b68b-cc42c03862b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24ae41f1-f8fb-4147-9278-5edd398743cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}